titleStmt.title: Match me these two: or The conviciton [sic] and arraignment of Britannicus and Lilburne. With an answer to a pamphlet, entituled, The parliament of ladies.

notesStmt.note: Britannicus = Marchamont Nedham and Thomas Audley.
A reply in part to: Neville, Henry. The ladies parliament (Wing L508).
Reproduction of the original in the British Library.
